<FlowDocument PagePadding="13" AllowDrop="True" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" 
xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"><Section>

<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">This sample illustrates the usage of summary types like Custom and DisplayIfDiscreteValuesEqual and its run-time features through PivotSchemaDesigner.</Paragraph>

<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center"><Image Source="Images/Summaries.png" Stretch="None" /></Paragraph></Section>
<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center" FontFamily="Cambria" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="14">PivotGrid with PivotSchemaDesigner showing ComputationInfo dialog for PivotItem</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List Margin="20,20,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">DisplayIfDiscreteValuesEqual summary type displays aggregated value in the Pivot Computation column when all the values are aggregated to be same, else PadString property value is displayed (By default, PadString property is set to *).</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Custom summary type is removed from the <Bold>Pivot Computation Info</Bold> dialog when any Custom summaries are loaded.</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Count summary type is loaded when <Bold>SummaryType</Bold> is set to <Bold>Custom</Bold> and no Custom Summaries are loaded.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

</FlowDocument>